      <title>欧洲央行称欧元区出口商面临持续的竞争力困境</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/euro-zone-exporters-facing-persistent-competitiveness-struggle-ecb-says-2024-09-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行周一发布的一项研究指出，未来数年，欧元区出口商将继续陷入困境，因为高昂的能源成本和低迷的劳动生产率增长将影响其竞争力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/euro-zone-exporters-facing-persistent-competitiveness-struggle-ecb-says-2024-09-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 08:07:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
